# FvwmButtons icon launcher:
DestroyFunc Launcher
AddToFunc Launcher
+ I DestroyModuleConfig $0Launch: *
+ I *$0Launch: Geometry 75x70
+ I *$0Launch: Columns 7
+ I *$0Launch: Rows    4
+ I *$0Launch: Frame   2
+ I *$0Launch: (5x3+1+0, Icon $1, Action (Mouse 1) `Exec exec $2`)
#+ I *$0Launch: Pixmap none      # To make icon transparent
+ I *$0Launch: (7x1+0+3, Title $0, Action (Mouse 1) `Exec exec $2`)
#+ I Style $0Launch HandleWidth 0, NoTitle
+ I Style $0Launch StaysonBottom, !Borders, NeverFocus, Sticky, FixedSize, FixedPosition
+ I Module FvwmButtons $3 $0Launch
+ I UpdateStyles

# Examples:
#Launcher XV          xv.xpm                               xv                "-g +0+100"
#Launcher RXVT        xterm.xpm                            "rxvt -bg black"  "-g +0+0"
Launcher Firefox      hicolor/48x48/apps/firefox.png       firefox           "-g +10-10"
Launcher Thunderbird  hicolor/48x48/apps/thunderbird.png   thunderbird       "-g +10-90"
Launcher Virtualbox   hicolor/48x48/apps/virtualbox.png    virtualbox        "-g +10-170"
Launcher Gimp         hicolor/48x48/apps/gimp.png          gimp              "-g +10-250"
Launcher Camera       hicolor/48x48/apps/guvcview.png      guvcview          "-g +10-330"
Launcher Ktechlab     hicolor/48x48/apps/ktechlab.png      ktechlab          "-g +10-410"
